What this Privacy Policy Covers
This Privacy Policy covers Pal Electronics Systems Ltd treatment of personally identifiable information that Pal Electronics Systems Ltd collects when you are on the website, and or using Pal Electronics Systems Ltd applications and or when you use Pal Electronics Systems Ltd services. This policy also covers Pal Electronics Systems Ltd treatment of any personally identifiable information that Pal Electronics Systems Ltd business partners share with Pal Electronics Systems Ltd.
This policy does not apply to the practices of companies that Pal Electronics Systems Ltd does not own or control, or to people that Pal Electronics Systems Ltd does not employ or manage.
What information is or may be collected from you
We will automatically receive and collect certain anonymous information in standard usage logs through our Web server, including computer-identification information obtained from "cookies," sent to your browser from:
an IP address, assigned to the computer and or mobile phone which you use
the domain server through which you access our service
the type of web browser you're using
the type of computer you're using
the type of mobile phone you're using
the location of Pal devices
