enable Bluetooth to find your PalGate devices
enable PalGate devices search and discovery
ONLY while using Auto Open feature: Collects location data in the background to enable Auto Open feature even when the app is closed or not in use.
SMS
enable mobile phone verification code auto parse
Camera
enable PalGate device QR code scan
enable take a picture of user for user profile
enable take a picture of device for application personalization
